<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About School</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.7.2/css/all.min.css">
</head>

<style>
    /* Mission & Vision Section */
    body {
        font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
        margin: 0;
        background-color: #f7fbff;
    }

    .hero img {
        width: 100%;
        height: auto;
        display: block;
        object-fit: cover;
    }

    .box {
        max-width: 1000px;
        width: 90%;
        margin: 60px auto;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
        border-radius: 15px;
        box-shadow: 0 6px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        padding: 40px 30px;
        transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out;
    }

    .box h1 {
        color: #0288d1; 
        font-size: 1.8rem;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
        text-align: center;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 1px;
    }

    .box p {
        color: #333;
        font-size: 1rem;
        line-height: 1.8;
        text-align: justify;
        margin-bottom: 40px;
        font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    }

    .box:hover {
        transform: scale(1.01);
        box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
    }

    /* Responsive Design */
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .box {
            padding: 25px 20px;
        }

        .box h1 {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
        }

        .box p {
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
    }

    @media (max-width: 480px) {
        .box h1 {
            font-size: 1.3rem;
        }

        .box p {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }
    }
</style>

<body>
    <%- include("partials/HomePageSchoolName") %>
    <%- include("partials/HomePageNavbar") %>

    <section class="hero">
        <img src="images/img4.jpg" alt="Rishikulam School Building">
    </section>

    <div class="box">
        <h1>MISSION</h1>
        <p>The mission of Rishikulam School is to provide a holistic and inspiring learning environment
            where students can achieve academic excellence while developing strong moral values,
            creativity, and leadership skills. We aim to prepare our students to face future challenges
            and become responsible global citizens.</p>

        <h1>VISION</h1>
        <p>Rishikulam School envisions becoming an educational institution that is a beacon of
            knowledge, innovation, and character building. We believe in nurturing each student's unique
            potential, fostering curiosity, and instilling a lifelong love for learning, enabling them
            to make positive contributions to society.</p>
    </div>

    <%- include("partials/HomePageContact") %>
    <%- include("partials/HomePageFooter") %>
</body>

</html>
